PrecisApproval of amendments made to the UNEMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS by C.E.I.C. which will increase the amount of the supplementary benefits provided to qualified claimants who attend a training course or program, and introduce a new section intitled "Disability Allowance" (section 111.1), effective February 3, 1991.
